Notice No. 01-172

May 18, 2001


TO:

All NYMEX and COMEX Division Members


RE:

Members' Forum on Brent Crude Oil Futures


All NYMEX and COMEX Division members are invited to an informational meeting

regarding the planned Brent crude oil futures contract on Wednesday, May 23,

at 3:30 PM, on the NYMEX Division trading floor.


This informational forum should not be confused with the special meeting of

stockholders of NYMEX Holdings, Inc., to elect equity holder directors and

fill two other vacant positions at 4:00 PM on the 10th floor.


The board and executive committee encourage all members to attend the

briefing on Brent futures.


